{
  "stem": "12494.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Orthodox Jewish community was much smaller and encompassed all of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish community was a-- segmented into three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a best Jewish community, there was a [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE] Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The best Jewish community was the largest one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] gymnasium, which was one of the better schools in the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I-- I entered that in the last year before graduation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and that, of course, brought me into contact with a lot of non-Orthodox Jews because most of my classmates were non-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course I was a kid to a large extent, and so, you know, you picked up these pieces of information very gradually.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember the Anschluss of Austria in 1938.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a great shock, at least to me, and-- other people may have expected it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were earlier indications.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Vacations, I remember we were in-- on vacation in Austria in the summer of 1934, my parents and my brother and I, and there was a very strong Nazi movement in Austria at the time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day we got the news that Chancellor Dollfuss of Austria was killed by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was nine years old at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a little bit hard for me to understand, but my dad explained what was going on, and I finally did understand.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you see, as of the age of-- of nine, we already dealt with antisemitism and Nazis and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But up to 1938, things were fairly peaceful in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was an unofficial-- and in some respects official-- antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mentioned the limitations at the universities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Jewish students went to Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They went to Austria, as long as Austria was possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
